class.name: gd_TopOpeBRepDS_Config
class.brief_description: Binding wrapper for the TopOpeBRepDS_Config enum from Open CASCADE Technology.
class.description:
This class provides Godot bindings for the TopOpeBRepDS_Config enum, which is used in Open CASCADE Technology to represent configuration states for BRep data structures.
